PrecisRe-appointment of Lisa Gilad, of St. John's, Newfoundland, as a full-time permanent member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montreal Regional Office) to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years, effective March 2, 1992.
